seo: Palo Alto Networks,PAN-OS,身份验证绕过漏洞,CVE-2025-0108
summary: 检测Palo Alto Networks PAN-OS系统中由于Nginx/Apache路径处理差异导致的身份验证绕过漏洞，该漏洞可能导致敏感数据泄露或系统被接管。
summary_en: Detect the authentication bypass vulnerability in Palo Alto Networks PAN-OS due to differences in Nginx/Apache path handling. This vulnerability may lead to sensitive data leakage or system takeover.
